## Dependencies

### Required Skills
- All skills are self-contained and do not require other skills to function

### Optional Dependencies
- Skills may reference other skills for enhanced functionality
- Pipeline flows orchestrate multiple skills together

### External Dependencies
- Skills may require specific tools or APIs (documented in each skill)

